@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tbbumd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.92 * tmp + 0.82)) / (wp.cos(tmp + 0.49) + wp.cos(v0 + 0.04)))
    v2 = (((tmp + 0.00 + v1 + 0.51) + (tmp + 0.81 + tmp + 0.32)) - v2)
    v2 = v1
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp + 0.38)))
    data[tid] = v0
